metadata.name: Norbert Nollack's Mona Lisa
metadata.description:
"Norbert Nollack's Mona Lisa"

AI artwork.

I depict a dystopian future in which people have to live among garbage and waste.

Art is not only about perfection and beauty.  
In my works I like to give space also to people who do not represent the standard concept of beauty: AI is helping me in doing this.

I find the imperfections of AI beautiful.
